{"tid":1841191,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[手足健康優先] 因應武漢肺炎疫情，民間集會團隊暫停舉行大型公眾活動一個月","createTime":"2020-01-25T07:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T08:47:50.000Z","uid":42194,"like":52,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"66454ec3e9dce3d160635f213ade5db828ef7068","tid":1841191,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zyk1xiF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZyk1xiF.jpg&h=d76bb691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因應2019新型冠狀病毒引發的武漢肺炎疫情持續惡化，為避免增加市民感染疾病風險，民間集會團隊宣佈，將暫停舉行大型公眾集會或遊行一個月，即至2020年2月24日為止，屆時會再作決定。<br />\n<br />\n雖然如此，民間集會團隊仍然會繼續協助素人舉辦小型公眾活動。任何活動組織者如有需要，請隨時聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n祝大家身體健康，新春平安。<br />\n<br />\n民間集會團隊<br />\n2020年1月25日<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n參與/洽詢合作：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKCATeam_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKCATeam_bot&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FfilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=a1fecf07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKCATeam_bot</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n我們的最新動向/合作洽詢：<br />\nFacebook：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCATeam%2F&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FfilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=a771a76a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam/</a><br />\nInstagram：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/HKCAT/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2FHKCAT%2F&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FfilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=75388065\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/HKCAT/</a><br />\nTwitter：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKCATeam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?